# Changes log for Data::FormValidator::Constraints::Words

0.07    2014-02-09
        - added USERNAME and PASSWORD, and associated methods.

0.06    2013-02-03
        - removed Artistic file.
        - change file dates changed to meet W3CDTF standards.
